sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Validator
    participant Handler
    participant UserDomain as User (Domain)
    participant DB as Database
    participant Events
    participant Cookie

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/auth/register
    Note right of Client: {email, password, displayName}

    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Extract payload
    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Create RegisterCommand

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(RegisterCommand)

    Mediator->>Validator: Validate(RegisterCommand)
    Validator->>Validator: Check email format
    Validator->>Validator: Validate password strength
    Validator->>Mediator: Validation passed ✓

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(RegisterCommand)

    Handler->>DB: Check email exists?
    DB-->>Handler: Not found ✓

    Handler->>UserDomain: User.Create(email, password)
    UserDomain->>UserDomain: Hash password (PBKDF2)
    UserDomain->>UserDomain: Create user entity
    UserDomain->>Events: Raise UserCreatedEvent

    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(user)
    DB-->>Handler: User saved ✓

    Handler->>Handler: Generate session token
    Handler->>DB: Create session
    DB-->>Handler: Session created ✓

    Handler->>Events: Publish UserRegisteredEvent

    Handler-->>Mediator: RegisterResponse
    Mediator-->>Endpoint: RegisterResponse

    Endpoint->>Cookie: WriteSessionCookie(token, expiresAt)
    Cookie-->>Client: Set-Cookie: meepleai_session

    Endpoint-->>Client: 200 OK
    Note left of Client: {user, expiresAt}
